These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
House: modern, victorian
City: prague, new-york
1. the person traveling to prague is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to new-york is the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| House   | victorian | modern |
| City     | new-york    | prague   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, amber
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, comedy
1. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Color   | amber | lavender        |
| Movie-Genre      | action  | comedy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, lilac
House: modern, craftsman
1. the modern house is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Color   | lilac    | azure |
| House   | modern | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, tennis
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, oliveros
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Sport   | golf      | tennis |
| Cigar       | ritmeester | oliveros    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, salsa
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, subway
1. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Music-Genre           | dubstep | salsa |
| Transport   | subway    | tram         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
There 2 different types of food: mango, corn
2 different games are played: chess, whist
1. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Food       | corn | mango  |
| Game   | whist  | chess |

