The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, reggae
1. the aristoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Cigar   | aristoff | prince   |
| Music-Genre         | ambient | reggae |

